snippet.title: beVaiR Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the new VR strategy game beVaiR by Randalyn Rage. 
– In a dystopian future is an AI the only one you can trust? 

Buy now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1711940/beVaiR/

Thanks to the wonderful @Haselnuuuss! 
https://www.twitch.tv/haselnuuuss 

More information: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1711940/beVaiR/

Official Site: https://bevairgame.com/ 
Publisher: https://randalynrage.com/ 

Follow beVaiR: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bevairgame/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/bevairgame/ 

Follow Randalyn Rage: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/randalynrage/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RandalynRage


Check out VaiR's Assistants:
Check out the Virtuoso behind the Music: https://www.queplay-music.com/
Check out the Magician behind the Virtual World: https://www.donaldkeeya.com/
Check out the Enthusiast behind the Moving Logo: https://klnpesch.de/
